// Still want to use the expert approach? 
//
// Be aware that it is much more tricky and does not boost the performances. 
//
// However, there are some contexts in which this low level approcah is required 
// and even mandatory. This is typically the case when you need to read or
// write several attributes on the same device in a single call. See Chapter II  
// "Reading one (or more) attribute(s) on a TANGO device" of the present tutorial
// to learn how to do so.
//   
